title: Server transfer just not there?..
body: So I just got 20e worth of RP in my account just to transfer to EU west and the option to transfer is just not there when i click on the account in the store. What do?

replies.body:
It's been mentioned time and time again on many of Riots platforms and articles.

Transfers are closed until the 20th November while pre-season rewards are being distributed.
[**Server transfers will still be closed until Nov 20**](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune). They've been closed for awhile due to end of season.
